            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "How was it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It was quite well made."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Thank you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Plachta!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sophie?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Plachta, what were you doing...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "As you can see, I was drinking tea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But you can't taste anything, can you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Wait... You can't taste anything...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yes. However, I can determine its composition."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see... That's... Quite surprising. I've never served a customer like this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "If I may suggest..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "If you change the tea leaves from 2 1/2 spoons to 2 1/3 spoons, you'll be able to draw out better flavor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I... I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll be going for today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Oh, she left..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I've never been given advice like that, either..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha... She's very unique."
        }
    ]
}